<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE053">
<l>moḻippaṭut ticaippiṉun terintuvē ṟicaippiṉu</l>
<l>meḻuttiya ṟiriyā veṉmaṉār pulavar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Learned men say that the nature of a sound</l>
<l>will not be altered</l>
<l>whether it is pronounced occurring in a word,</l>
<l>or appears pronounced otherwise.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
